# Website Preview Walkthrough

Dev server running at `http://localhost:3000/`

## Insight Detail Pages (New Feature)
Clicking on an Insight card's title now navigates to a dedicated reading page. The page preserves the site's minimalist aesthetic, beautifully renders the full Markdown content of the research articles, and includes a "Back to Insights" button.

![Insight Detail Top](file:///C:/Users/ASUS/.gemini/antigravity/brain/381aa514-9a77-4b13-bbda-b6fc0cf91ff9/insight_detail_top_1772941196195.png)

At the bottom of each full-length article, a non-commercial license footer has been added as requested:
![Insight Detail Bottom](file:///C:/Users/ASUS/.gemini/antigravity/brain/381aa514-9a77-4b13-bbda-b6fc0cf91ff9/insight_detail_bottom_1772941218001.png)

