## Frontmatter Bug Fix
Fixed frontmatter parsing in [markdown.ts](file:///d:/Project%20&%20Data/minimal-personal-website/src/utils/markdown.ts) — the regex used `\n` but Windows files have `\r\n` endings, causing raw YAML metadata to render as card text.

